task-manager/
│
├── auth-service/          ← handles sign up, login, JWTs, etc.
├── task-service/          ← handles tasks (CRUD, drag/drop)
├── notification-service/  ← handles email reminders, queue
└── client/                ← React frontend (talks to others via REST)

Each backend service will be a small Node.js + Express + MongoDB app.
They’ll communicate via REST API calls or (optionally later) message queues.

